  "texts": [
    "This benchmark is designed to test LLMs on eight specific tasks that measure their capacity for understanding, reasoning, and explaining within the domain of chemistry.",
    "These tasks include name and property prediction, yield and reaction prediction, retrosynthesis, text-based molecule design, molecule captioning, and reagents selection.",
    "For example, in the text-based molecule design task, LLMs are challenged to generate a Simplified Molecular Input Line Entry System (SMILES) code based on given inputs, showcasing their ability to apply chemical knowledge in practical scenarios.",
    "The evaluation of five prominent LLMs -ChatGPT, GPT-4, Davinci-003, Llama, and Galactica-was conducted in both zero-shot and few-shot in-context learning settings, revealing varied competencies across the tasks.",
    "Specifically, the analysis showed competitive performances in two tasks, selective competitiveness in three, and noncompetitiveness in the remaining three."
  ],
